<subSubSection id="C33C6516C937FFBDF9EBF92CFB07F542" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8B99369DC937FFBDF9EBF92CFB07F542" blockId="36.[151,1436,1781,2024]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis id="B952EA8FC937FFBDF9EBF92CFE8BF50A" bold="true" box="[151,274,1781,1808]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
“Corallum monopodial and pinnulate; attached to hard substrates by an adhesive basal plate. Pinnules simple, bilateral and either subopposite or alternating. Spines usually simple, triangular, compressed; rarely with knob-like bifurcations at the apex. Polyps 
<quantity id="4CDE9B78C937FFBDFB0DF8E7FD57F542" box="[625,718,1854,1880]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.0" metricValueMax="9.0" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" unit="mm" value="6.0" valueMax="9.0" valueMin="3.0">3–9 mm</quantity>
in transverse diameter” (
<bibRefCitation id="EFB74B6CC937FFBDFA9BF8E7FB0BF542" author="Opresko, D. M." box="[999,1170,1854,1880]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" pagination="411 - 442" refId="ref48859" refString="Opresko, D. M. (2002) Revision of the Antipatharia (Cnidaria: Anthozoa). Part II. Schizopathidae. Zoologische Mededelingen, 76, 411 - 442." type="journal article" year="2002">Opresko, 2002</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C33C6516C937FFBCF9BBF8BBFF53F2E1" lastPageId="37" lastPageNumber="38" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B99369DC937FFBCF9BBF8BBFF53F2E1" blockId="36.[151,1436,1781,2024]" lastBlockId="37.[151,1436,153,287]" lastPageId="37" lastPageNumber="38" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis id="B952EA8FC937FFBDF9BBF8BBFEA2F566" bold="true" box="[199,315,1890,1916]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Remarks.</emphasis>
The genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C264D1EC937FFBDF8C6F8BBFD4FF566" authority="Brook, 1889" authorityName="Brook" authorityYear="1889" box="[442,726,1890,1916]" class="Anthozoa" family="Schizopathidae" genus="Bathypathes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Antipatharia" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B952EA8FC937FFBDF8C6F8BBFDDDF566" box="[442,580,1890,1916]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Bathypathes</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFB74B6CC937FFBDFB37F8BBFD4FF566" author="Brook, G." box="[587,726,1890,1916]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" refId="ref46539" refString="Brook, G. (1889) Report on the Antipatharia collected by HMS Challenger during the years 1873 - 1876. Zoology, 32, 1." type="journal volume" year="1889">Brook, 1889</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
currently contains eight species of monopodial corals with simple pinnules arranged bilaterally in two rows [
<taxonomicName id="4C264D1EC937FFBDFBE5F85EFC0DF5BA" authority="Brook, 1889" authorityName="Brook" authorityYear="1889" box="[665,916,1926,1952]" class="Anthozoa" family="Schizopathidae" genus="Bathypathes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Antipatharia" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="species" species="patula">
<emphasis id="B952EA8FC937FFBDFBE5F85EFC99F5BA" box="[665,768,1926,1952]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">B. patula</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFB74B6CC937FFBDFA7AF85FFC0DF5BA" author="Brook, G." box="[774,916,1926,1952]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" refId="ref46539" refString="Brook, G. (1889) Report on the Antipatharia collected by HMS Challenger during the years 1873 - 1876. Zoology, 32, 1." type="journal volume" year="1889">Brook, 1889</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="4C264D1EC937FFBDFAE3F85EFB21F5BA" authority="Thomson, 1905" authorityName="Thomson" authorityYear="1905" box="[927,1208,1925,1952]" class="Anthozoa" family="Schizopathidae" genus="Bathypathes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Antipatharia" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="species" species="bifida">
<emphasis id="B952EA8FC937FFBDFAE3F85EFC66F5BA" box="[927,1023,1926,1952]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">B. bifida</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFB74B6CC937FFBDFD7AF85FFB21F5BA" author="Thomson, J. A. &amp; Simpson, J. J." box="[1030,1208,1925,1952]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" pagination="93 - 106" refId="ref50006" refString="Thomson, J. A. &amp; Simpson, J. J. (1905) Report of the Antipatharia collected by Prof. Herdman at Ceylon, 1902. Ceylon Pearl Oyster Report, 4, 93 - 106. [not consulted]" type="journal article" year="1905">Thomson, 1905</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="4C264D1EC937FFBDFDBFF85EFF42F5DE" authority="(Brook, 1889)" authorityName="Brook" authorityYear="1889" baseAuthorityName="Brook" baseAuthorityYear="1889" class="Anthozoa" family="Schizopathidae" genus="Bathypathes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Antipatharia" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="species" species="conferta">
<emphasis id="B952EA8FC937FFBDFDBFF85EFAA6F5BA" box="[1219,1343,1926,1952]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">B. conferta</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFB74B6CC937FFBDFC32F85FFF4AF5DE" author="Brook, G." pageId="36" pageNumber="37" refId="ref46539" refString="Brook, G. (1889) Report on the Antipatharia collected by HMS Challenger during the years 1873 - 1876. Zoology, 32, 1." type="journal volume" year="1889">Brook, 1889</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="4C264D1EC937FFBDF994F872FDBCF5DE" authority="Totton, 1923" authorityName="Totton" authorityYear="1923" box="[232,549,1962,1988]" class="Anthozoa" family="Schizopathidae" genus="Bathypathes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Antipatharia" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="species" species="platycaulus">
<emphasis id="B952EA8FC937FFBDF994F872FE13F5DE" box="[232,394,1962,1988]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">B. platycaulus</emphasis>
Totton, 1923
</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="4C264D1EC937FFBDFB4DF872FCE6F5DE" authority="Pasternak, 1977" authorityName="Pasternak" authorityYear="1977" box="[561,895,1962,1988]" class="Anthozoa" family="Schizopathidae" genus="Bathypathes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Antipatharia" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="species" species="galatheae">
<emphasis id="B952EA8FC937FFBDFB4DF872FD59F5DE" box="[561,704,1962,1988]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">B. galatheae</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFB74B6CC937FFBDFBB4F873FCE6F5DE" author="Pasternak, F. A." box="[712,895,1962,1988]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" pagination="157 - 164" refId="ref49495" refString="Pasternak, F. A. (1977) Antipatharia. Galathea Report. Scientific results of the Danish Deep-Sea Expedition round the world 1950 - 52, 14, 157 - 164." type="journal article" year="1977">Pasternak, 1977</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="4C264D1EC937FFBDFAF0F872FB23F5DE" authority="Schultze, 1903" authorityName="Schultze" authorityYear="1903" box="[908,1210,1962,1988]" class="Anthozoa" family="Schizopathidae" genus="Bathypathes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Antipatharia" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="species" species="erotema">
<emphasis id="B952EA8FC937FFBDFAF0F872FB9EF5DE" box="[908,1031,1963,1988]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">B. erotema</emphasis>
Schultze, 1903
</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="4C264D1EC937FFBDFDBBF872FF4BF5F2" authority="Opresko, 2001" authorityName="Opresko" authorityYear="2001" class="Anthozoa" family="Schizopathidae" genus="Bathypathes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Antipatharia" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="species" species="bayeri">
<emphasis id="B952EA8FC937FFBDFDBBF872FAB6F5DE" box="[1223,1327,1962,1988]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">B. bayeri</emphasis>
Opresko, 2001
</taxonomicName>
; and 
<taxonomicName id="4C264D1EC937FFBDF86CF816FDDBF5F2" authority="(Gravier, 1918)" authorityName="Gravier" authorityYear="1918" baseAuthorityName="Gravier" baseAuthorityYear="1918" box="[272,578,1997,2024]" class="Anthozoa" family="Schizopathidae" genus="Bathypathes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Antipatharia" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="species" species="robusta">
<emphasis id="B952EA8FC937FFBDF86CF816FE1FF5F2" box="[272,390,1998,2024]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">B. robusta</emphasis>
(Gravier, 1918)
</taxonomicName>
]. (Note: the species previously known as 
<taxonomicName id="4C264D1EC937FFBDFD67F816FA9BF5F2" authority="Broook" authorityName="Broook" box="[1051,1282,1998,2024]" class="Anthozoa" family="Schizopathidae" genus="Alternatipathes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Antipatharia" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="species" species="alternata">
<emphasis id="B952EA8FC937FFBDFD67F816FBB5F5F2" box="[1051,1068,1999,2024]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">B</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="B952EA8FC937FFBDFD40F817FB3AF5F2" box="[1084,1187,1998,2024]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">alternata</emphasis>
Broook
</taxonomicName>
, was recently transferred to the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C264D1EC936FFBCF8DFFF40FDC9F2A9" authorityName="Molodtsova &amp; Opresko" authorityYear="2017" box="[419,592,153,179]" class="Anthozoa" family="Schizopathidae" genus="Alternatipathes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Antipatharia" pageId="37" pageNumber="38" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B952EA8FC936FFBCF8DFFF40FDC9F2A9" box="[419,592,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Alternatipathes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
—see 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB74B6CC936FFBCFBE9FF40FC6FF2A9" author="Molodtsova, T. N. &amp; Opresko, D. M." box="[661,1014,153,179]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38" pagination="349 - 365" refId="ref48440" refString="Molodtsova, T. N. &amp; Opresko, D. M. (2017) Black corals (Anthozoa: Antipatharia) of the Clarion-Clipperton Fracture Zone. Marine Biodiversity, 47 (2), 349 - 365. https: // doi. org / 10.1007 / s 12526 - 017 - 0659 - 6" type="journal article" year="2017">Molodtsova and Opresko, 2017</bibRefCitation>
) The genus can be distinguished from 
<taxonomicName id="4C264D1EC936FFBCF9EBFF64FEB0F2CD" authorityName="Brook" authorityYear="1889" box="[151,297,189,215]" class="Anthozoa" family="Schizopathidae" genus="Schizopathes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Antipatharia" pageId="37" pageNumber="38" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B952EA8FC936FFBCF9EBFF64FEB0F2CD" box="[151,297,189,215]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Schizopathes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
mainly due to the presence of the basal disk and longer pinnules in the medial portion of the corallum.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C33C6516C936FFBCF9BBFEDDFD6BF305" box="[199,754,260,287]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="8B99369DC936FFBCF9BBFEDDFD6BF305" blockId="37.[151,1436,153,287]" box="[199,754,260,287]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">
<emphasis id="B952EA8FC936FFBCF9BBFEDDFEF8F305" bold="true" box="[199,353,260,287]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Distribution.</emphasis>
Cosmopolitan (
<bibRefCitation id="EFB74B6CC936FFBCFB6FFEDCFD7FF305" author="Molodtsova, T. N." box="[531,742,261,287]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38" pagination="3 - 7" refId="ref48147" refString="Molodtsova, T. N. (2014) Deep-sea fauna of European seas: An annotated species check-list of benthic invertebrates living deeper than 2000 m in the seas bordering Europe. Antipatharia. Invertebrate Zoology, 11, 3 - 7. https: // doi. org / 10.15298 / invertzool. 11.1.02" type="journal article" year="2014">Molodtsova, 2014</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
